data.revised_prompt: A realistic representation of a grand library as dense fog shrouds the early autumn morning outside. The muted sunlight strains to break through the thickness of the fog, creating a mystical and serene ambiance. The library is adorned with tall wooden shelves stuffed with books of all sizes and colors, accompanied by comfortable reading spots. Long tables with classic green-shaded desk lamps are dispersed throughout the area. Spiral staircases intertwine within this space, leading to the library's upper levels. The elegant architecture adds to the grandeur of the scene, engulfed by a symphony of silence.
